<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="MediaWiki.E3.83.98.E3.83.AB.E3.83.97">MediaWikiヘルプ</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/ja&amp;veaction=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: MediaWikiヘルプ" class="mw-editsection-visualeditor">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-divider"> | </span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manual:Installation_guide/ja&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8" title="Edit section: MediaWikiヘルプ">edit source</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
