<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Newcomers_guide_to_installing_on_Windows" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Newcomers guide to installing on Windows">初心者向けガイド</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Streamlined_Windows_Install_Guide" title="Special:MyLanguage/Manual:Streamlined Windows Install Guide">効率化されたガイド</a></li>
